een-and-white-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181258\/bedroom-pop-colour-combination-green-and-white-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Blissful green &#038; white combination in a tranquil bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/pop-designs-for-bedroom\/\">Pop Designs For Bedroom<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Unique POP Design Colour Combination for Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Discover the charm of plus-minus design with this eye-catching pop colour combination for the living room that strategically balances contrasts. Enhance your area with the allure of woody beige and classic white to create a culturally enriching atmosphere.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181412\/pop-colour-combination-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Mix of woody beige and white pop colour combinations for living room creates a culturally enriching atmosphere\" class=\"wp-image-52361\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181412\/pop-colour-combination-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181412\/pop-colour-combination-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181412\/pop-colour-combination-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181412\/pop-colour-combination-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Think beyond wallpapers for your living room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Yet Elegant: Grey &amp; White Hall POP Colour Combination<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Welcome the beauty of simplicity with the classic grey and white hall POP colour combination. The design emanates subtle elegance, fostering a sophisticated ambience that strikes a balance between refinement and simplicity at the core of your house.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181334\/grey-and-white-hall-pop-colour-combination.jpg\" alt=\"Grey and white hall pop colour combination for a simple look\" class=\"wp-image-52357\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181334\/grey-and-white-hall-pop-colour-combination.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181334\/grey-and-white-hall-pop-colour-combination-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181334\/grey-and-white-hall-pop-colour-combination-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181334\/grey-and-white-hall-pop-colour-combination-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Simplicity beckons elegance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sun-kissed Vibes: A Bright POP Colour Combination<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bring the sun inside with this POP ceiling colour combination. Sun-kissed vibes permeate your room with the striking partnership of yellow and white. Revel in cosiness and warmth, as this mixture creates a glowing atmosphere that reflects the happy spirit of sunshine in your house.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181430\/yellow-and-white-pop-colour-combination.jpg\" alt=\"Yellow and white pop colour combination in living room reflects the happy spirit of sunshine\" class=\"wp-image-52363\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181430\/yellow-and-white-pop-colour-combination.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181430\/yellow-and-white-pop-colour-combination-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181430\/yellow-and-white-pop-colour-combination-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181430\/yellow-and-white-pop-colour-combination-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Say hello to sun-kissed vibes<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contrasting Orange POP Design Colour Combination With White<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Salute, vivid contrasts! The effervescent neon orange and white design on the ceiling scores all the hits. It is a striking combination that enlivens the room and gives your house a vibrant atmosphere. Can there be any blue with such a perky vibe? Absolutely not.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181343\/orange-pop-design-colour-combination-with-white.jpg\" alt=\"Vibrant kids' bedroom with an orange pop design colour combination with white creates a lively atmosphere\" class=\"wp-image-52358\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181343\/orange-pop-design-colour-combination-with-white.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181343\/orange-pop-design-colour-combination-with-white-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181343\/orange-pop-design-colour-combination-with-white-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181343\/orange-pop-design-colour-combination-with-white-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Orange energy for your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">POP Ceiling Colour Combination Enhanced With Perfect Lighting<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make a statement in monotone combined with the right lighting solutions. The monochromatic faux ceiling enhances the sophistication of the room. It is a classic combination that brightens your space and gives your house more depth and elegant charm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181352\/pop-ceiling-colour-combination-with-lighting.jpg\" alt=\"Monotone pop ceiling colour combination with lights in the living room enhances the sophistication\" class=\"wp-image-52359\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181352\/pop-ceiling-colour-combination-with-lighting.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181352\/pop-ceiling-colour-combination-with-lighting-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181352\/pop-ceiling-colour-combination-with-lighting-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181352\/pop-ceiling-colour-combination-with-lighting-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">POP designs work well with false ceilings<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Beautiful Carved POP Design: Colour Combinations For Kid\u2019s Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a wacky environment for your kids! The vibrant walls are enhanced with lovely carvings that make your child&#8217;s room feel more playful. It&#8217;s an imaginative blend that is lively and ignites creativity. The cute moon crescent and the stars add glamour to the ceiling and infuse an exuberant vibe overall.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181326\/carved-pop-design-colour-combination-for-kids-room.jpg\" alt=\"Kids' room with a green, white, and brown pop design colour combination, moon and star carvings add a whimsical touch\" class=\"wp-image-52356\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181326\/carved-pop-design-colour-combination-for-kids-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181326\/carved-pop-design-colour-combination-for-kids-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181326\/carved-pop-design-colour-combination-for-kids-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181326\/carved-pop-design-colour-combination-for-kids-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Playful carvings for your kid\u2019s room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Vibrant Drawing Room POP And Wall Colour Combination<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a cordial environment with the richness of brown tones. This POP and wall colour combination exudes warmth and makes it an inviting space for hosting social gatherings. Check out the minimalistic decor that is beautifully offset by larger-than-life furniture and decor pieces that exude a confident and assured vibe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181317\/brown-and-white-pop-and-wall-colour-combination.jpg\" alt=\"Brown and white pop and wall colour combination in a stylish drawing room\" class=\"wp-image-52355\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181317\/brown-and-white-pop-and-wall-colour-combination.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181317\/brown-and-white-pop-and-wall-colour-combination-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181317\/brown-and-white-pop-and-wall-colour-combination-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181317\/brown-and-white-pop-and-wall-colour-combination-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Don\u2019t be afraid of living large<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/drawing-room-interiors\/pop-design-for-drawing-room\/\">Pop Design For Drawing Room<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dramatic and Bold: Hall POP Colour Combination for Maximalists<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make a statement with this hall POP colour combination that is eye-catching and borders on audacious. It is an elegant combination that draws attention and, with its striking charm, creates a dramatic atmosphere in your house. It is perfect for those who like a fuller look to their home and aren&#8217;t shy of experimenting with more prominent motifs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/13181308\/bold-pop-color-combination-for-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Bold pop colour combination for hall\" class=\"wp-image-52354\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\